These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, social-worker, scientist, teacher
There 4 different types of food: lemon, kale, tomato, cranberry
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, scrabble, domino
1. the person eating kale is the teacher##1
2. the person eating tomato is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person eating kale is the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the police-officer is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | lemonade   | milk  | almond-milk  |
| Job   | social-worker    | teacher    | police-officer      | scientist    |
| Food   | cranberry | kale | tomato | lemon |
| Game     | domino  | poker       | canasta    | scrabble     |

