.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, cain, montecristo, bolivar
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, rose, daisy, marigold
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, blue, chestnut, light-blue
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, coffee, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is the person drinking tea##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who likes chestnut and the person drinking lemonade##2
6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who likes light-blue##2
7. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | bolivar | cain    | montecristo  | davidoff    |
| Flower   | poppy      | rose  | marigold  | daisy |
| Color           | light-blue      | chestnut       | blue      | ebony       |
| Beverage         | tea    | mirinda | coffee | lemonade |

