.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
City: hamburg, liverpool, venice, paris
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, havana, swisher, vegafina
There are 4 different favourite beverages: veniceade, tea, fanta, coffee
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, poker, go
1. the person drinking fanta is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the person drinking tea is the vegafina-smoker##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is between the pall-mall-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
9. the swisher-smoker is between the person traveling to venice and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City        | liverpool | venice     | hamburg   | paris     |
| Cigar       | havana   | pall-mall   | swisher | vegafina |
| Beverage         | veniceade   | fanta | coffee       | tea    |
| Game   | poker    | canasta | chess  | go    |

