.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, avocado, cauliflower, raspberry
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, pall-mall, old-henry, baccarat
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, zinnia, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, punk, jazz, folk
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the baccarat-smoker is the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the fan folk##1
 4. the fan d&b is on the far left##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the fan d&b##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the fan punk##1
10. the person eating avocado is between the person who growstulip and the person eating raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Food           | eggplant  | raspberry | avocado     | cauliflower |
| Cigar   | baccarat | bolivar  | old-henry | pall-mall       |
| Flower           | lily       | bellflower    | zinnia      | tulip           |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | punk   | folk   | jazz         |

