.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, hedgehog, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, motorbike, bus
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, scrabble, canasta
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, woodworking, card-games
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person driving the roller is the person playing chess##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person playing mah-jongg##2
10. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | turtle         | hedgehog         | snake     | frog      |
| Transport           | motorbike | bus | ship    | roller     |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | scrabble       | canasta    | chess       |
| Hobby         | dancing     | woodworking       | card-games | drawing |

