2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person eating lettuce and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the victorian house and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
9. the person eating peach is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday           | november | october | may  | june |
| Food   | peach      | asparagus       | lettuce     | onion      |
| Hobby   | puzzles   | dancing      | reading   | board-games   |
| House         | cape-cod   | colonial    | futuristic | victorian   |

